::KitKat::

She chuckled softly to herself. "I agree with you on that one."
She turned to see Terorsaur enter the cave.
She looked at Quickstrike and nodded towards Terrorsaur. "Who is big red 
over there? I have seen him sleeping in the corner over there, but I never 
met him. Who and what is he?"

"And who is this Wild that you refer to? Is he one of us?"

--Original Message---
From: Talon Harvilicz  <wilddance_mare@h...>
Date: Wed Jul 5, 2000 5:10pm
Subject: Neo Beast Wars


Quickstrike:


Quickstrike chuckled lowly at KitKat. "That's what ah was thinkin'." he
whispered back. "If they do somethin' stupid, ah'm throwin' their kiesters
out in th' Wild. That might straighten 'em out."

At the mouth of the cave, he saw Terrorsaur fly enter in his beast mode. The
dactyl had been out and about lately.
